What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Solid State Drive Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Solid State Drive Market

Solid state drive market size is valued at USD 119.82 million by 2028 is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 14.76% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on solid state drive provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth.

Solid state drive is a type of a nonvolatile storage device which helps to store data on solid state flash memory. In the solid state drive the digital data is stored straightforwardly in silicon NAND flash memory devices. It has no automatic moving which improves stability in opposing physical shock or mechanical failure and enhances performance.

The high adoption of SSD in data centers is expected to influence the growth of solid state drive market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the rise in the penetration for high end cloud computing and rapid decline in the cost of SSD which will gain advantage over HDD thus are also anticipated to flourish the growth of the solid state drive market. Furthermore, the rise in the initiative for deployment of 5G technology in developing nations and high demand from consumer electronics products are also likely to positively impact the growth of the market. Moreover, the rise in the penetration of high-end cloud computing and rise in the e-commerce activities across the globe are also expected create a huge demand for solid state drive as well as lifting the growth of the solid state drive market.

However, the high cost of the product and the smaller life span of SSDs are expected to act as the major limitations for the growth of solid state drive in the above mentioned forecasted period, whereas the various design complexity can challenge the solid state drive market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

Likewise, the rise in the application scope of the SSD in automotive sector, rise in the use of social media and high demand for sufficient capacity to store content are expected to create various new opportunities that will lead to the growth of the solid state drive market in the above mentioned forecasted period.

